" Pager-like binds
bind u scrollpage -0.5
bind d scrollpage  0.5

" Unbind find
unbind <C-f>

" Buffers
bind <C-u> undo
bind <S-x> bdelete
bind cs tabopen -c school
bind cm tabopen -c school https://moodle.njit.edu
bind cc tabopen -c school https://canvas.njit.edu
bind cp tabopen -c personal
bind ca tabopen -c shopping

" Terminal
set editorcmd $TERMINAL -e "$EDITOR %f"
